( 2012–15 ) " O.W.C.A. FILES " Section::::"O.W.C.A. Files " .
" O.W.C.A. Files " is an hour - long special on Disney XD after the series finale .
While the episode was set to air during the regular season , it was later announced by Disney on May 7 , 2015 , that the show would end with Last Day of Summer on June 12 , 2015 , and that the episode would air as a stand - alone special on the Disney XD network .
